{"tid":2080862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【倒數4日】71 反國安法遊行 最後召集","createTime":"2020-06-26T18:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T06:28:52.000Z","uid":90601,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1bf166a023305d462ccd3ea0c5a2ac08033beb79","tid":2080862,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T18:10:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">海外議會街頭 缺一不可<br />\n香港人，行動！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【#71遊行 堅持五大訴求 反抗國安惡法】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U61qyy6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU61qyy6.jpg&h=f45455a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vVnEC0N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvVnEC0N.jpg&h=efab0292&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JQ5Sdy8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJQ5Sdy8.jpg&h=adde143b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期｜2020 年 7 月 1 日 星期三<br />\n集合地點｜維園集合<br />\n集合時間｜2PM<br />\n起步時間｜3PM<br />\n遊行終點｜金鐘添美道<br />\n*遊行正申請不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n#71Rally<br />\nFIVE DEMANDS, NOT ONE LESS<br />\nRESIST NATIONAL SECURITY LAW<br />\n<br />\nDate｜1st July 2020, Wednesday<br />\nStarting Point｜Victoria Park <br />\nAssemble｜2PM<br />\nStart｜3PM<br />\nEnd Point｜Tim Mei Avenue, Admiralty<br />\n*Letter of No Objection Pending<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">be water 流動如水<br />\nbe water 洶湧如浪<br />\nbe water 堅硬如冰<br />\nbe water 消失如霧</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a84f2bd1f85fa92da7f957d9dd82bfff34d92631","tid":2080862,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T18:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe0d53c9e8fb826ab5a5f1ced6cfb107cf65da9","tid":2080862,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T18:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512727c556d26af1f5a2d741061a670d8d4c106c","tid":2080862,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T18:21:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2b67c7f25f05f7500cfb32e0f06ebcabb502920","tid":2080862,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T18:22:12.000Z","msg":"今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">李柱銘不代表我，我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉比美國睇，咪比條廢老騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"6ea843a6d06456e5d162eef99d556af0d5f9269c","tid":2080862,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T18:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2633ddd986409ab9fd3deb579d7b071fdbea5919","tid":2080862,"uid":67940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T18:29:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40fdcf15b847c91bd8c52794c68b8492c47494ef","tid":2080862,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T18:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45380ce09d5f6f29a8a099fcf98d4ec55f049103","tid":2080862,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T18:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada92a233da98de8bc621e6c869819a664b7f576","tid":2080862,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T18:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f221d4a19b647cd4303f4c172bad91547a31733","tid":2080862,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T19:03:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98c11b08d8479e88446f14921a1ca48fb65a42da","tid":2080862,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T19:03:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bfb3fa59059dba4ba355420fc5727ecb6643cd9","tid":2080862,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T19:05:25.000Z","msg":"大大力咁推"},{"pid":"1575a8eefbaa20eca7a72743d6111e8c2ecad66f","tid":2080862,"uid":49018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"